## Skill Loading

**Progressive Disclosure:**

- Skills load context incrementally
- Use `/skill` command to invoke installed skills

**Anthropic Official Skills:**

```bash
/plugin marketplace add anthropics/skills
/plugin install document-skills@anthropic-agent-skills
/plugin install frontend-design@anthropic-agent-skills
```

**Creating Custom Skills:**

```bash
~/.claude/skills/my-skill/SKILL.md
```

## Running Multiple Sessions

**Separate Directory Sessions:**

```bash
cd /path/to/project && claude
```

**Git Worktrees:**

```bash
git worktree add ../project-feature -b feature-name
cd ../project-feature && claude
```

## Advanced CLI Flags

- `--dangerously-skip-permissions`: Skip permission prompts (CAUTION)
- `--verbose`: Detailed logging
- `--model sonnet`: Start with specific model
- `--continue`: Resume most recent conversation
- `--allowedTools "Bash,Read,Write"`: Pre-approve tools
- `--max-turns N`: Limit agentic turns
- `--print`: Non-interactive mode
